	&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;Bir adet&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;riddex plus fare ve haşare kovucu&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
