	&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;Bir adet 12 li&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;magic hair saç tebeşiri.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
