	&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;1 Adet &lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Su Geçirmez Telefon Kılıfı Universal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
