&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Paket İçeriği:&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 8.5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

