	&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;Bir adet süngerli barfiks&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;Bir adet montaj paketi&lt;/li&gt;
