	&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; outline: 0px; margin: 5px 0px 5px 10px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc;&quot;&gt;1 adet Tutma Yakalama Aparatı&lt;/li&gt;
